Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.24,0:00:19.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾吉由 什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛得到同夥傳來的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:26.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說已經得知柯楠王子的行蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,羅澤 是時候復仇了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:03.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:05.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起來像公主嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.45,0:01:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是羅澤嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈…不是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:12.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是假冒的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.57,0:01:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許碰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.19,0:01:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不　是真的羅澤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不許笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.94,0:01:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過沒想到 帝國的王子居然要和羅澤結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是布拉德 竟然能辦成這件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要跟著布拉德 我們也都能出人頭地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.65,0:01:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德回來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.92,0:01:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是布拉德！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:47.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布拉德！你看你看！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像不像公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:51.49,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}悲しみに囚われた魂達
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.59,0:02:51.49,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}為悲傷所困的靈魂們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:03:01.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}終わらない憎しみが叫びだす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:03:01.27,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}因無盡的憎恨而呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:06.58,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}迷いの森を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.31,0:03:06.58,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}穿過迷惘的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.26,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}世界照らしに行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.26,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}我們將去照亮世界
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:15.65,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絶望抱きしめるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:15.65,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}會去擁抱絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.37,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}諦めていない証
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.37,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}說明還未放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:26.25,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}孤独超えたら信じあえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.52,0:03:26.25,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}當我們跨越孤獨便可互相信任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.12,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}絆離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:29.12,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}不要放開這份情感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.94,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望という眩しい重さに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.22,0:03:33.94,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}希望炫目而又沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.64,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}負けない情熱この手にある
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:39.64,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}手中握有不被壓倒的熱誠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:46.20,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}想い  光へ  何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:46.20,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}思念化作光芒 無論多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.14,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}命尽き果てるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:50.14,OPCH,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur2}直至生命耗盡
